苏州市一小区内，一小学五年级小孩手持弓弩自曝虐猫，小孩还说以杀猫为傲，准备在网上买自动杀猫机。孩子母亲表示尊重其爱好。 该小孩还表示：（虐猫组织）少部分是初中的，还有一部分是六年级的，最小是四年级的，分散在各个学校。 视频截图。图源：法治进行时 视频截图。图源：法治进行时 9 月 6 日，苏州市金鸡湖街道办事处发布情况通报： 9 月 5 日，有网友反映一儿童手持弓弩自述打猫猎猫，街道开展了核实调查。经核查，发现儿童陈某某曾有过使用工具打猫的行为，但是不存在视频中其所述的「小团体」「打猫小分队」等情况。经批评教育，该名儿童已经认识到行为不妥，并主动上交了打猫所用工具。 我们将联合学校教育引导孩子要有爱心、善待动物。感谢社会各界的关心和关爱。苏州通报「某小区内一小学生手持弓弩虐猫」：有过打猫行为，不存在小团体，已批评教育 _ 金鸡 _ 儿童 _ 进行时"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d48c33fd273f1f3889a24ace8373c8ae_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666370998"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz+71lO2Yxe5SEAMaCTExMDM2MDM5OSCG1uq2BjAAOC9ABHIJNjY2MzcwOTk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1725700015.966204", "card_id": "Q_666355585", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么看待伊拉克地铁招标，德法等四国中标，中国企业未中标?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9651881394a14979ab0f0726a51fea6d_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666355585"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz+71lO2Yxe5SEAMaCTExMDM1Njk5OCD+7em2BjAAOBxABXIJNjY2MzU1NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1725700015.967682", "card_id": "Q_275825797", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89